                "name": "Wand Magic",
                "ability_type": "Supernatural",
                "ability_type_abbrev": "Su",
                "text": "A wrathplated clockwork mage\u2019s wand crystal allows it to cast spells as if using a spell trigger magic item (CL 9th). It can cast 1st-level spells at will, 2nd-level spells four times per day, and 3rd-level spells twice per day.<br/><br/><i>Evocation</i>: 1st\u2014<a href=\"SpellDisplay.aspx?ItemName=magic%20missile\" style=\"text-decoration:underline\"><i>magic missile</i></a>, <a href=\"SpellDisplay.aspx?ItemName=shocking%20grasp\" style=\"text-decoration:underline\"><i></i></a> (DC 11); 2nd\u2014 <a href=\"SpellDisplay.aspx?ItemName=gust%20of%20wind\" style=\"text-decoration:underline\"><i>gust of wind</i></a> (DC 13), <a href=\"SpellDisplay.aspx?ItemName=scorching%20ray\" style=\"text-decoration:underline\"><i>scorching ray</i></a>; 3rd\u2014<a href=\"SpellDisplay.aspx?ItemName=fireball\" style=\"text-decoration:underline\"><i>fireball</i></a> (DC 14)"
